name: Culling Streets
description:
Dive into an all-new unmatched, chaotic 15v15 competitive experience and rise to the top of the ranks. Slice, Shoot, Beat, or Run Over your enemies till you are the last one left.

Play different game modes similar to typical free-for-alls, Team Deathmatch, search and destroy, and many others!

Unlock powerful weapons and "OVERPOWERED" killstreaks on your way to the top!

Customize your look uniquely to your liking... Gotta stand out from the competition!

Uncover many tactics and master the one you prefer on your rise.
